# elemai

An AI LLM coding library.

## Installation

```bash
pip install elemai
```

## Quick Start

```python
import elemai

```

## Development

Install development dependencies:

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

Run tests:

```bash
pytest
```

Format code:

```bash
black .
isort .
```
